Browser runner gap: `policy-crypto-host-random.harness-args` is
currently ignored when the test runs through `browser-test-runner.mjs`
(see NOTES.md `browser-runner-ignores-harness-args`).  The runner
currently outputs the no-policy state.  Unskip when the browser runner
maps harness-args to URL params (e.g. via the existing `?policies=`
opt-in mechanism).
